---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="SeaTac Airport Limo Service | SEA Transfers | Emerald City Limos"
  description="Professional Seattle-Tacoma International Airport limo service. Flat-rate transfers, 24/7 flight tracking, meet and greet at baggage claim. Book your SEA airport car service now."
  keywords="seatac airport limo, sea-tac airport car service, seattle airport transportation, SEA airport transfer, seatac limo service, seattle tacoma international airport limo"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 z-10"></div>
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1436491865332-7a61a109cc05?w=1920&h=1080&fit=crop&q=85"
      alt="Seattle-Tacoma International Airport limo service"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      width="1920"
      height="1080"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="inline-block bg-emerald-700 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">SEA Airport</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 drop-shadow-2xl">
        Seattle-Tacoma Airport <span class="text-[#d4af37]">Limo Service</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-gray-100">
        Flat-rate transfers, 24/7 flight tracking and meet and greet at baggage claim
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/book-now" class="bg-[#d4af37] hover:bg-[#b8941f] text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all inline-block">
          BOOK SEATAC TRANSFER
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+12065959675" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-emerald-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all inline-block">
          (206) 595-9675
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Stats -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-emerald-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">24/7</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Available</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">$89+</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Starting Price</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">30+</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Cities Served</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">4.9</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Star Rating</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About SeaTac + Service Details -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            SeaTac Airport Limo Service by <span class="text-emerald-700">Emerald City Limos</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Seattle-Tacoma International Airport (SEA) is the Pacific Northwest's busiest airport, handling over 50 million passengers annually. Whether you are arriving for business or departing on vacation, navigating SeaTac can be stressful — especially during peak travel hours.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Emerald City Limos provides premium flat-rate limo service to and from SeaTac Airport across all of King County, Snohomish County, and Pierce County. Our professional chauffeurs track your flight in real time, adjusting pickup times automatically for delays or early arrivals.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            For arrivals, your chauffeur meets you at baggage claim with a name sign, assists with luggage, and escorts you to your waiting vehicle. No waiting in taxi lines, no surge pricing, no surprises.
          </p>
          <a href="/book-now" class="inline-block bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all">
            Book Your SeaTac Transfer
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What is Included</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Real-Time Flight Tracking</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We monitor your flight and adjust pickup automatically</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Baggage Claim Meet and Greet</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Chauffeur waiting with name sign inside the terminal</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">60 Minutes Free Wait Time</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Complimentary waiting after your flight lands</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Flat-Rate Pricing</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">No surge pricing, no hidden fees, price locked at booking</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Luxury Fleet</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Cadillac Escalade, Mercedes S-Class and executive sedans</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Infant Car Seats Available</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Pre-installed at no extra charge when requested</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Popular Routes -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Popular SeaTac Airport Routes</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Flat-rate pricing from your city to SeaTac Airport</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Seattle to SeaTac</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $89</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">14 miles, approx 20-35 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Bellevue to SeaTac</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $99</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">16 miles, approx 25-40 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Redmond to SeaTac</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $109</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">22 miles, approx 30-45 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Kirkland to SeaTac</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $109</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">20 miles, approx 30-45 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Everett to SeaTac</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $129</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">35 miles, approx 40-55 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Tacoma to SeaTac</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $99</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">27 miles, approx 30-45 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm mt-6">Prices are estimates. Get an exact quote when booking.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SeaTac Airport Info -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">SeaTac Airport Information</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Everything you need to know about your arrival or departure</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Arrivals Pickup</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Your chauffeur will meet you inside the terminal at baggage claim with a name sign. After collecting your luggage, they will escort you to the vehicle in the designated pickup area on the ground transportation level.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Terminal A/B:</strong> Ground level, Door 1</li>
            <li><strong>International Arrivals:</strong> Level 1, baggage claim area</li>
            <li><strong>Wait Time:</strong> 60 minutes complimentary after landing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Departures Pickup</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">For departures, your chauffeur arrives at your location 15 minutes early. They will assist with luggage to the departure level at SeaTac and ensure you arrive with plenty of time for check-in and security.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Recommended Lead Time:</strong> 2.5 hours domestic, 3.5 hours international</li>
            <li><strong>Drop-off:</strong> Departure level at your airline terminal</li>
            <li><strong>Luggage Assistance:</strong> Always included</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">SeaTac airport limo service questions answered</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How much does a limo from SeaTac to Seattle cost?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Our flat-rate SeaTac to Seattle limo service starts from $89. The exact price depends on your pickup location and vehicle type. You get a locked-in price at booking with no surge pricing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What happens if my flight is delayed?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We track all flights in real time. If your flight is delayed, your chauffeur automatically adjusts their arrival time. You will not be charged extra for flight delays.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Where does my driver meet me at SeaTac?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">For arrivals, your chauffeur meets you inside the terminal at baggage claim holding a sign with your name. You do not need to go outside or look for a car yourself.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you offer SeaTac airport service 24 hours?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, we operate 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year including holidays. Early morning and late night flights are no problem.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I bring an infant car seat?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. We offer complimentary pre-installed infant car seats and booster seats. Just request one when booking and it will be ready in the vehicle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-900 to-emerald-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Book Your SeaTac Airport Limo Today</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-gray-200">
        Flat-rate pricing, 24/7 service, professional chauffeurs. The best way to get to and from SeaTac Airport.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/book-now" class="bg-[#d4af37] hover:bg-[#b8941f] text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all inline-block">
          BOOK NOW
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+12065959675" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-emerald-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all inline-block">
          Call (206) 595-9675
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
